```python
def most_frequent_words(sentence):
    counts = {}
    words = sentence.lower().split()
    for word in words:
        counts[word] = counts.get(word, 0) + 1
    max_count = max(counts.values())
    return [word for word, count in counts.items() if count == max_count]
```

